# Test bbuild files

## Dependency relationships

These have inter-dependencies to test the dependency code paths.

- `fakeblock.bbuild` depends on `fakeblock-songs`
- `fakeblock-songs.bbuild` makedepends on `fakeblock-song-gen`
- `fakeblock-song-gen.bbuild` has no dependencies, runtime or otherwise

## e2e test infrastructure relationship

- e2e setup symlinks these files into a shared repository directory (`${CARGO_TARGET_TMPDIR}/e2e/common/repo`)
- e2e setup generates repository indexes to access them via repository references
- Tests can reference them either via `repo_path!(...)` for a file path or `repo_url!(...)` for networking.
